OL,3,CMan arrested 22 years on from murder
OL,4,Cof Tyrone Clarke in Leeds
OL,6,FOfficers investigating the 2004 murder
OL,7,Fof Tyrone Clarke in Leeds have
OL,8,Farrested a man.
OL,10,FTyrone Clarke, 16, was stabbed to
OL,11,Fdeath in Brett Gardens, Beeston, after
OL,12,Fbeing chased by a gang on 22 April
OL,13,F2004.
OL,15,FDuring the attack, he was assaulted
OL,16,Fwith weapons including metal poles and
OL,17,Fplanks of wood.
OL,19,FThe attack saw the conviction of three
OL,20,Fmen and a 17-year-old boy, who were
OL,21,Fjailed in 2005.
